**5. Build Dependency Map**

The following sequence governs what must be built before what. Cursor
prompts must follow this order --- attempting to build later modules
before earlier ones will produce code that cannot connect to its
dependencies.

  --------- ------------------- --------------------- --------------------
  **Build   **Module**          **Depends On**        **Key Deliverable**
  Order**                                             

