**6. Open Architectural Questions**

The following questions do not block the build start but must be
resolved before the relevant module is built.

  -------- --------------------------------------- ---------------- --------------
  **\#**   **Question**                            **Blocks**       **Priority**

  1        Monorepo tooling: Turborepo vs. Nx vs.  Project scaffold High ---
           simple npm workspaces?                  (Build Order 1)  resolve before
                                                                    first Cursor
                                                                    prompt

  2        What is the exact member cap for the    Monetization /   Medium ---
           family subscription tier?               Stripe           needed before
                                                   integration      payment build
                                                   (Phase 3)        

  3        AI rate limits per user per day ---     AI Assistant     High ---
           what are the cost-sustainable           build (Build     define before
           thresholds?                             Order 10)        assistant goes
                                                                    live

  4        COPPA compliance approach: parental     Invitation       High --- legal
           consent flow design?                    system for minor input required
                                                   profiles (Build  
                                                   Order 5)         

  5        What US states / regions are in scope   Data residency,  Medium ---
           at launch? (GDPR scope?)                privacy policy,  needed before
                                                   legal            public launch

  6        Moderation strategy for harmful or      Platform         Medium ---
           abusive family content?                 policies, trust  needed before
                                                   & safety         public launch
                                                   features         
